WEBVTT

01:35.900 --> 01:40.980
=Love Beyond the Grave=
(Adapted from the novel by Li Qingran)

01:41.260 --> 01:43.980
=Episode 4=

01:45.910 --> 01:46.750
Stay alert.

02:51.040 --> 02:51.900
Xiaoxiao,

02:51.900 --> 02:52.900
how's it going?

02:53.860 --> 02:54.700
It's all right.

02:54.700 --> 02:55.620
We're safe now.

03:41.230 --> 03:42.270
Ancestors bless us.

03:42.460 --> 03:43.550
Ancestors bless us.

03:53.230 --> 03:54.070
Xiaoxiao,

03:54.300 --> 03:55.580
what on earth is going on?

03:56.110 --> 03:57.300
Maybe our ancestors wouldn't

03:57.950 --> 03:59.110
want their descendants

03:59.110 --> 03:59.950
to be bullied.

04:13.350 --> 04:14.460
This place is creepy.

04:15.020 --> 04:15.860
Let's leave now.

04:16.550 --> 04:17.820
Yes. Let's move.

04:17.820 --> 04:18.890
- Let's go.
- Come on.

04:22.180 --> 04:26.340
(Shuozhou)

04:27.030 --> 04:28.740
Why are there more people coming?

04:29.260 --> 04:30.230
It's Tabai Army.

04:30.790 --> 04:32.990
I wonder how long they'll stay.

04:33.350 --> 04:35.550
How about we flee the town?

04:35.820 --> 04:36.660
Don't say that.

04:37.030 --> 04:39.670
If the Chong Army returns, we'll suffer.

04:48.500 --> 04:49.340
Xiaoxiao,

04:49.990 --> 04:51.500
I think we're in Shuozhou.

05:04.060 --> 05:05.300
Stop looking. Come back in.

05:10.620 --> 05:11.500
As you expected,

05:11.910 --> 05:13.350
some Chong soldiers ambushed Miss He.

05:14.150 --> 05:15.110
Captain Han was there,

05:15.380 --> 05:16.790
so Miss He survived.

05:17.620 --> 05:18.550
In that case,

05:18.950 --> 05:19.790
is Captain Han

05:19.790 --> 05:21.030
cleared of suspicion?

05:22.620 --> 05:23.860
In an ambush,

05:24.590 --> 05:25.430
they must have had

05:25.910 --> 05:26.820
more soldiers than us.

05:27.220 --> 05:28.060
How did Han Lingqiu

05:28.060 --> 05:28.900
manage to repel them?

05:31.740 --> 05:32.590
It was pretty strange.

05:33.620 --> 05:35.030
We were lurking around there.

05:35.670 --> 05:36.710
- Stay alert!
- I saw them

05:36.710 --> 05:37.820
become outnumbered

05:38.110 --> 05:38.950
and it looked real.

05:39.500 --> 05:40.790
I had intended to help them.

05:41.180 --> 05:42.180
But many blue fireballs

05:42.180 --> 05:43.380
appeared out of nowhere

05:43.670 --> 05:45.180
and only attacked our enemies.

05:49.060 --> 05:49.940
General,

05:49.940 --> 05:50.780
Miss He has arrived.

05:57.380 --> 05:58.220
Captain Han,

05:58.380 --> 05:59.220
are you all right?

06:00.260 --> 06:01.230
We got ambushed.

06:01.910 --> 06:02.750
But we're fine now.

06:04.740 --> 06:06.460
(Lin Mansion)

06:06.470 --> 06:07.310
Mission completed.

06:07.710 --> 06:08.820
Miss He has been delivered.

06:09.860 --> 06:11.150
I heard you had been ambushed.

06:11.940 --> 06:13.620
Thanks to your desperate fight,

06:14.150 --> 06:15.380
Miss He has survived.

06:15.620 --> 06:16.460
Actually,

06:17.260 --> 06:18.300
I take no credit for that.

06:18.740 --> 06:20.150
Things were a little bit weird.

06:20.500 --> 06:21.340
Weird?

06:22.470 --> 06:23.420
Not at all.

06:24.180 --> 06:25.590
Our ancestors showed their power.

06:27.670 --> 06:28.510
General Duan,

06:28.860 --> 06:29.790
since Shuozhou Campaign,

06:30.300 --> 06:31.140
how have you been?

06:33.990 --> 06:35.500
(Lin Mansion)
You got ambushed.

06:36.180 --> 06:37.590
I was really worried.

06:40.500 --> 06:42.230
I came here on your orders.

06:43.790 --> 06:44.740
But on my way,

06:47.110 --> 06:48.790
I nearly lost my life.

06:49.350 --> 06:50.190
How could that be?

06:50.620 --> 06:52.420
You've always been blessed.

06:53.150 --> 06:54.620
Captain Meng once told me

06:54.790 --> 06:55.820
she met something wicked.

06:56.030 --> 06:57.110
But when you appeared,

06:57.860 --> 06:59.180
it was gone.

07:00.300 --> 07:01.500
During the ambush,

07:01.990 --> 07:03.150
you were there with my men.

07:03.620 --> 07:04.820
And thanks to the blessing,

07:06.300 --> 07:07.350
you arrived safely.

07:08.910 --> 07:09.940
What a coincidence.

07:10.820 --> 07:11.660
Isn't it?

07:14.300 --> 07:15.140
Yes.

07:16.590 --> 07:18.300
Maybe you're right, General.

07:19.260 --> 07:20.100
I am

07:20.940 --> 07:22.470
blessed.

07:33.740 --> 07:34.710
(This body)

07:35.150 --> 07:36.150
(won't last much longer.)

07:44.470 --> 07:45.310
Miss He.

07:49.350 --> 07:50.190
I think

07:52.990 --> 07:53.830
you have a fever.

07:56.470 --> 07:57.310
General Duan,

07:58.060 --> 07:59.420
are you testing me again?

08:03.300 --> 08:04.590
Can you really not feel it?

08:09.110 --> 08:10.470
Oh, I'm really sick.

08:25.650 --> 08:26.500
Xiaoxiao,

08:26.500 --> 08:27.340
you're finally awake.

08:27.590 --> 08:28.590
Are you feeling better?

08:31.260 --> 08:32.950
(This body is so weak.)

08:41.540 --> 08:42.380
Where are we?

08:43.310 --> 08:44.470
According to the General,

08:44.950 --> 08:46.230
we are in Mr. Lin's mansion,

08:46.950 --> 08:48.860
the richest man in Shuozhou.

08:56.230 --> 08:57.660
Miss He, since you're awake,

08:58.190 --> 08:59.230
let the physician

09:00.140 --> 09:01.140
give you a checkup.

09:21.740 --> 09:22.620
Have you been

09:22.830 --> 09:23.950
feeling fatigued

09:24.740 --> 09:26.620
with weak limbs and abdominal pain?

09:28.110 --> 09:29.260
A little bit, I think.

09:30.470 --> 09:31.660
Sensitive to wind and cold,

09:31.900 --> 09:32.740
with a dull appetite?

09:34.500 --> 09:35.340
A little bit.

09:36.260 --> 09:37.140
A weak chest?

09:39.380 --> 09:40.260
A little bit, too.

09:44.470 --> 09:46.540
Do you feel sick or upset?

09:49.950 --> 09:50.790
A little bit.

09:51.590 --> 09:52.430
Physician,

09:53.500 --> 09:55.020
since she's so seriously ill,

09:55.660 --> 09:57.260
please prescribe properly

09:57.540 --> 09:58.620
and make sure she recovers.

10:15.500 --> 10:16.340
Miss He,

10:16.780 --> 10:17.620
it's medicine time.

10:21.230 --> 10:22.070
Um...

10:22.380 --> 10:23.310
Xiaoxiao,

10:23.310 --> 10:24.950
I'll go buy you some preserves.

10:28.110 --> 10:29.590
General, you don't need to bother

10:29.860 --> 10:31.110
bringing me medicine yourself.

10:31.380 --> 10:32.710
You contributed to my army.

10:33.190 --> 10:34.030
So, your illness

10:34.380 --> 10:35.540
isn't a minor thing.

10:37.310 --> 10:38.950
Is it a rule of your army?

10:39.430 --> 10:40.950
If Commandant Xia falls ill,

10:41.260 --> 10:42.740
will you also send him medicine?

10:44.590 --> 10:45.590
No, actually.

10:47.140 --> 10:48.740
Meng Wan told me you like me.

10:49.710 --> 10:50.950
So, bringing you medicine

10:51.470 --> 10:52.310
can make you happier.

11:03.660 --> 11:04.500
Sorry, sorry.

11:10.380 --> 11:11.860
Hey, if you keep wiping,

11:11.860 --> 11:12.780
you'll rub my skin raw.

11:36.950 --> 11:38.830
I don't think you like me.

11:39.230 --> 11:40.430
I think you like my skull.

11:42.260 --> 11:43.620
I've been wandering about for years

11:44.000 --> 11:45.560
and I just have some quirks.

11:47.380 --> 11:48.500
Let's both drop the act,

11:49.590 --> 11:50.430
Miss He.

11:52.380 --> 11:53.230
Or I should call you

11:55.990 --> 11:57.710
"a miraculous lady lacking five senses".

12:06.230 --> 12:07.380
I can't compare to you,

12:07.660 --> 12:08.500
General.

12:08.950 --> 12:09.830
You've never trained.

12:10.710 --> 12:11.740
But when you were 19,

12:11.740 --> 12:13.140
you escaped from bandits

12:13.470 --> 12:14.780
and went home alone from afar.

12:15.470 --> 12:17.020
Commandant Wu has fought wars for years.

12:17.540 --> 12:18.710
But within just a few moves,

12:18.710 --> 12:19.620
you took him down.

12:20.140 --> 12:20.990
Over seven years in Daizhou,

12:20.990 --> 12:22.310
all who knew you are now dead

12:22.310 --> 12:23.380
and dead men tell no tales.

12:23.740 --> 12:24.590
Besides...

12:27.310 --> 12:28.260
Red birds are to...

12:29.990 --> 12:30.950
Red birds are to burn

12:31.740 --> 12:32.580
all living beings.

12:33.830 --> 12:34.780
Red birds are to burn

12:35.590 --> 12:37.110
all living beings.

12:38.740 --> 12:39.950
You know Aphorisms of Cangshen.

12:41.260 --> 12:42.110
Are you really the one

12:42.110 --> 12:43.780
from before you turned twelve?

12:46.950 --> 12:47.950
You checked up on me.

12:48.950 --> 12:49.860
Right back at you.

12:50.660 --> 12:51.780
You did the same.

12:53.590 --> 12:54.430
So,

12:55.310 --> 12:56.230
what's your conclusion?

12:57.830 --> 12:58.900
Then, do you have

12:58.900 --> 12:59.950
any conclusion about me?

13:07.900 --> 13:08.740
We are both

13:08.740 --> 13:10.660
puppets in disguise.

13:11.710 --> 13:13.310
Let's not break the ice.

13:18.380 --> 13:19.830
There may be more ice.

13:21.780 --> 13:22.950
If we break some,

13:24.710 --> 13:25.710
there will be more.

13:28.830 --> 13:30.020
You used me as bait.

13:30.950 --> 13:32.540
What if I helped your enemies instead?

13:34.590 --> 13:35.620
From what I've seen,

13:36.780 --> 13:38.310
they don't have pretty skulls.

13:39.230 --> 13:40.190
They can't attract you

13:40.190 --> 13:41.110
like I do.

13:44.620 --> 13:45.860
Are you so sure?

13:48.590 --> 13:49.540
I'm not sure.

13:50.470 --> 13:51.500
But I'm a born gambler

13:52.540 --> 13:53.500
and I'm always lucky.

13:54.950 --> 13:56.230
I always land on my feet.

13:57.590 --> 13:59.380
So, you believe you won't lose?

13:59.900 --> 14:01.070
If I don't gamble, I won't.

14:01.990 --> 14:02.860
But in that case,

14:03.950 --> 14:05.070
I'll never win, either.

14:07.110 --> 14:08.380
Since you're a wagering man,

14:09.500 --> 14:10.540
let's make a wager.

14:12.900 --> 14:13.740
On what?

14:18.900 --> 14:19.900
On whether you are

14:19.900 --> 14:20.990
the real Duan Xu.

14:30.950 --> 14:32.140
(Real Duan Xu.)

14:35.900 --> 14:36.740
Stop running!

14:39.380 --> 14:40.470
How dare you steal from me?

14:40.780 --> 14:41.740
I'm going to kill you!

14:43.190 --> 14:44.030
Don't you dare.

14:54.540 --> 15:01.860
(Liang)

15:01.860 --> 15:03.590
Xu sent you to shadow Captain Han.

15:03.860 --> 15:05.110
I don't know if you're injured.

15:05.430 --> 15:06.270
Here, take this.

15:09.020 --> 15:09.990
I'm fine.

15:11.310 --> 15:12.150
Take it.

15:13.190 --> 15:14.030
I'm really fine.

15:14.350 --> 15:15.190
You keep it.

15:15.470 --> 15:16.710
Use it next time you get hurt.

15:17.310 --> 15:18.150
Come on.

15:18.620 --> 15:19.500
Are you cursing me?

15:20.380 --> 15:22.110
No, no. I don't mean that.

15:33.350 --> 15:34.590
Miss He...

15:35.110 --> 15:35.950
How is she now?

15:36.110 --> 15:37.020
The physician checked,

15:37.020 --> 15:37.860
saying she was fine.

15:38.050 --> 15:38.900
She's in Lin Mansion.

15:38.900 --> 15:39.740
What?

15:40.380 --> 15:41.900
She stays with the General?

15:42.350 --> 15:43.860
Yes. What's wrong?

15:44.650 --> 15:45.500
Hey, think about it.

15:45.500 --> 15:46.470
Why does Xu care so much

15:46.470 --> 15:47.430
about her?

15:48.310 --> 15:49.190
Because she helps us

15:49.200 --> 15:50.260
with weather observations.

15:50.260 --> 15:51.430
Do you think she's pretty?

15:51.430 --> 15:52.270
Yes.

15:58.470 --> 15:59.310
You're pretty!

15:59.660 --> 16:00.590
I didn't ask that!

16:00.830 --> 16:02.310
You don't judge me.

16:04.330 --> 16:05.190
I do think

16:05.190 --> 16:06.310
you look very good.

16:15.660 --> 16:18.060
(Enjoy the Beauty)

16:24.020 --> 16:25.140
(In the face of enemies,)

16:25.500 --> 16:26.780
(how can you still laugh?)

16:45.260 --> 16:46.780
(Well disguised.)

16:47.310 --> 16:48.950
(No clues have been left)

16:48.950 --> 16:49.790
(about his identity.)

17:29.540 --> 17:30.780
(That's a good physique.)

17:37.500 --> 17:38.580
(How does he have)

17:38.580 --> 17:39.870
(so many old and new scars?)

17:52.820 --> 17:54.260
(He's quite vigilant.)

18:13.500 --> 18:15.340
(Well, he remains chaste.)

19:38.140 --> 19:41.860
(Yan Ke, Right Hand of the Void)

20:03.190 --> 20:04.030
No more hiding.

20:04.500 --> 20:05.340
Come out.

20:09.710 --> 20:10.550
Chang.

20:11.340 --> 20:12.630
You let her go?

20:14.260 --> 20:15.190
Your Lordship,

20:15.190 --> 20:16.870
Yinyin and I didn't mean to escape.

20:17.500 --> 20:18.670
By the Golden-wall Decrees,

20:19.580 --> 20:21.630
spirits shall not
enter the Mortal World.

20:22.340 --> 20:23.910
How dare you defy the decrees

20:24.470 --> 20:25.820
issued by the Sovereign?

20:30.400 --> 20:31.260
I can make you

20:31.260 --> 20:32.820
continue as the Vice Lord.

20:33.630 --> 20:34.470
Or

20:34.910 --> 20:36.820
you can turn to ashes with her.

20:37.060 --> 20:38.100
Make your choice.

20:41.870 --> 20:42.820
Chang.

20:51.060 --> 20:51.900
Yinyin.

20:58.340 --> 20:59.180
Chang.

21:31.340 --> 21:33.230
When you first became a spirit,

21:34.020 --> 21:35.580
I saved you.

21:36.740 --> 21:37.580
Yinyin,

21:38.910 --> 21:39.780
I'm sorry.

22:07.990 --> 22:08.830
Remember.

22:09.630 --> 22:11.820
This is your own choice.

22:15.180 --> 22:18.460
(Liang)

22:20.300 --> 22:21.820
We were kept in ignorance.

22:22.230 --> 22:23.390
How could he be so childish

22:23.390 --> 22:24.430
about military operations?

22:25.190 --> 22:26.030
What if...?

22:27.820 --> 22:28.950
Commandant Wu, you're back.

22:29.430 --> 22:30.540
Let me introduce the one

22:30.950 --> 22:32.300
who contributed to our army.

22:36.580 --> 22:38.470
You lied about us attacking Yuzhou.

22:38.740 --> 22:40.230
Actually, we attacked Shuozhou.

22:40.470 --> 22:41.950
Why? Try to trick me?

22:41.950 --> 22:43.190
Now you get me back.

22:43.200 --> 22:44.040
You tell me.

22:44.040 --> 22:44.880
What about Yuzhou?

22:44.880 --> 22:45.750
Commandant Wu!

22:46.470 --> 22:47.540
The General doesn't need

22:47.540 --> 22:48.780
your approval to deploy troops!

22:50.390 --> 22:51.870
Commandant Wu, calm down.

22:52.430 --> 22:53.340
The tea is very hot.

22:59.150 --> 23:00.340
Any complaints?

23:01.580 --> 23:02.990
I don't have complaints.

23:03.430 --> 23:04.340
Indeed.

23:04.340 --> 23:05.820
We won this battle.

23:06.020 --> 23:06.860
But you...

23:07.470 --> 23:08.340
You were never honest

23:08.340 --> 23:09.430
with any of us.

23:09.950 --> 23:11.780
Soldiers can risk their lives,

23:12.060 --> 23:13.820
but no one wants a senseless death.

23:13.990 --> 23:15.340
You have a special way

23:15.340 --> 23:16.820
of conducting military operations

23:16.820 --> 23:18.150
and playing tricks on enemies.

23:19.020 --> 23:19.910
But with people,

23:20.430 --> 23:21.670
you're pretty flaky

23:21.670 --> 23:22.520
and quite evasive.

23:22.530 --> 23:23.390
I don't accept that!

23:27.100 --> 23:27.940
Commandant Wu,

23:28.470 --> 23:29.710
you always show your emotions

23:30.580 --> 23:31.780
and you've guarded the border.

23:32.630 --> 23:33.910
Enemies know you very well.

23:34.540 --> 23:35.910
If I had told you about the feint,

23:36.540 --> 23:37.390
they might have known.

23:37.990 --> 23:38.830
Besides,

23:40.150 --> 23:41.390
there was a huge gap in strength

23:41.390 --> 23:42.300
between both sides.

23:42.990 --> 23:44.190
Cornered soldiers fight best!

23:45.710 --> 23:47.100
If they hadn't fought

23:47.100 --> 23:48.100
with the resolve to die,

23:49.060 --> 23:50.630
a backup plan wouldn't help at all.

23:51.150 --> 23:52.340
So what?

23:52.820 --> 23:54.390
We couldn't have won

23:54.580 --> 23:55.870
without the red birds

23:55.870 --> 23:57.630
that happened to fly by.

23:58.800 --> 24:00.430
Those birds didn't happen to fly by.

24:01.020 --> 24:02.580
They were part of the General's plan.

24:03.060 --> 24:03.950
Those were pigeons

24:04.150 --> 24:05.670
the General had painted

24:05.670 --> 24:06.910
with the flame pattern.

24:09.710 --> 24:10.550
What?

24:11.430 --> 24:12.740
Before the war, I asked Meng Wan

24:13.950 --> 24:15.430
to search nearby pigeon farms.

24:16.380 --> 24:17.780
(Liang)

24:17.780 --> 24:19.060
Chong people believe in Cangshen.

24:20.540 --> 24:21.870
In Aphorisms of Cangshen,

24:22.260 --> 24:23.630
red birds with the flame pattern

24:23.630 --> 24:25.190
will be sent down from the heavens.

24:25.950 --> 24:27.670
Chong people firmly believe red birds

24:28.300 --> 24:29.190
will bring disasters.

24:31.100 --> 24:31.940
So,

24:32.300 --> 24:33.820
I had those pigeons prepared.

24:34.990 --> 24:36.190
When the wind blew at sunrise,

24:36.870 --> 24:38.150
I had them released.

24:39.470 --> 24:41.060
(You're so familiar with their belief.)

24:41.910 --> 24:43.500
(Is it because you're knowledgeable)

24:43.990 --> 24:45.990
(or is it because you're a Chong man?)

24:45.990 --> 24:47.390
General, you're quite knowledgeable

24:47.780 --> 24:48.910
while I'm merely uneducated.

24:49.230 --> 24:50.580
I'm no match for you.

24:51.610 --> 24:52.470
Now,

24:52.470 --> 24:53.780
Awo'erqi of the Chong Army

24:53.780 --> 24:54.620
and reinforcements

24:54.620 --> 24:55.710
will arrive in days.

24:56.430 --> 24:57.270
I believe

24:57.500 --> 24:58.870
you've had a surefire plan.

24:59.470 --> 25:01.540
Will you share it with us, please?

25:01.780 --> 25:02.670
Yeah.

25:09.390 --> 25:10.710
Miss He, what do you suggest?

25:14.780 --> 25:15.740
This is Miss He

25:15.740 --> 25:17.230
who offers us weather predictions.

25:18.100 --> 25:19.230
During Shuozhou Campaign,

25:19.710 --> 25:21.540
she predicted the weather conditions.

25:23.060 --> 25:24.540
General, do you have to

25:24.990 --> 25:26.230
stop their reinforcements?

25:26.780 --> 25:27.620
Of course.

25:28.470 --> 25:29.390
Then how about

25:31.580 --> 25:33.260
you blow up the Guanhe River?

25:33.260 --> 25:34.300
Blow up the Guanhe River?

25:34.820 --> 25:35.780
What?

25:35.910 --> 25:37.230
How can we do that?

25:37.710 --> 25:39.060
It's still very cold.

25:39.580 --> 25:40.910
What's the use of blowing it up?

25:41.240 --> 25:42.100
In a few days,

25:42.100 --> 25:43.190
the river will freeze again.

25:43.670 --> 25:45.230
That area has a pleasant climate.

25:45.580 --> 25:47.020
The river doesn't freeze in winter.

25:47.580 --> 25:48.540
But this year,

25:48.540 --> 25:49.910
the rare freezing weather

25:50.060 --> 25:51.150
has led to the frozen river.

25:52.020 --> 25:53.230
But in my opinion,

25:54.060 --> 25:55.100
the freezing weather

25:56.230 --> 25:57.630
won't last much longer.

25:58.870 --> 26:00.430
In ten days, the temperature will soar,

26:00.950 --> 26:02.020
the cold will recede,

26:02.470 --> 26:03.390
and it will get warm.

26:04.060 --> 26:05.020
If you blow up the river

26:05.020 --> 26:06.020
before that,

26:06.630 --> 26:07.470
I don't think

26:07.670 --> 26:08.580
it will freeze again

26:08.580 --> 26:10.100
anytime soon.

26:16.300 --> 26:17.710
I think it's a good idea.

26:18.430 --> 26:19.580
Blow up the Guanhe River?

26:20.430 --> 26:21.270
And then?

26:21.950 --> 26:23.100
Go back to Liangzhou?

26:24.740 --> 26:25.710
Commander Qin ordered.

26:27.470 --> 26:28.780
We'll defend Shuozhou at all costs

26:29.340 --> 26:30.820
and defeat their reinforcements.

26:31.740 --> 26:32.630
We must not retreat.

26:32.910 --> 26:34.150
Defend Shuozhou at all costs?

26:37.390 --> 26:39.670
We must not retreat?

26:42.100 --> 26:43.670
This is no joke.

26:44.430 --> 26:45.500
If we blow up the river

26:45.740 --> 26:47.190
without going back to Liangzhou,

26:47.740 --> 26:49.470
every single person here

26:49.470 --> 26:50.630
will end up dead!

26:52.060 --> 26:53.630
Is it really Commander Qin's order?

26:53.910 --> 26:55.100
Or did you fake it

26:55.710 --> 26:56.820
for military merit?

26:58.020 --> 27:00.300
Ambition is never satisfied!

27:06.580 --> 27:07.820
The city under our feet

27:08.670 --> 27:09.740
belongs to Great Liang.

27:10.630 --> 27:12.060
Thirty years ago, Great Liang troops

27:12.060 --> 27:13.500
were utterly defeated right here.

27:14.710 --> 27:15.550
North Chong troops

27:16.390 --> 27:17.430
occupied the 17 Prefectures

27:17.430 --> 27:18.300
without scruples.

27:20.230 --> 27:21.390
They even marched south,

27:22.630 --> 27:23.740
massacring Liangzhou.

27:27.540 --> 27:28.990
After tough wars

27:29.790 --> 27:30.630
and bloody battles,

27:30.630 --> 27:31.870
we finally made it back here.

27:33.060 --> 27:34.740
Are we just going to give in?

27:36.300 --> 27:37.230
Since it's our duty,

27:39.230 --> 27:40.430
don't be so worried.

27:41.230 --> 27:42.070
We will win.

27:45.540 --> 27:46.710
Can we win just because

27:48.060 --> 27:49.630
you think we will?

27:55.150 --> 27:56.020
Commandant Wu,

27:57.390 --> 27:58.710
I'm indeed dictatorial.

27:59.580 --> 28:00.710
But so far,

28:02.190 --> 28:03.060
I have never lost.

28:04.260 --> 28:05.100
Have I?

28:08.190 --> 28:09.030
Fine.

28:10.020 --> 28:11.780
I'll trust you one more time.

28:12.950 --> 28:14.710
No one here is afraid to die.

28:14.710 --> 28:16.100
But we shouldn't die in vain!

28:17.580 --> 28:20.950
If we fail to repel our enemies,

28:21.710 --> 28:22.950
I will haunt your family

28:23.500 --> 28:25.020
even if I die!

28:25.150 --> 28:26.340
Don't worry, Commandant Wu.

28:27.300 --> 28:28.540
If you die, so will I.

28:31.300 --> 28:32.430
I'm counting on you all.

28:50.060 --> 28:51.470
Wu Shengliu hates you so much

28:51.680 --> 28:52.520
possibly because

28:52.530 --> 28:53.540
you're too good-looking.

28:55.580 --> 28:56.420
You flatter me.

28:57.150 --> 28:57.990
It's my honor.

28:59.540 --> 29:00.820
Actually,

29:01.190 --> 29:02.260
Commandant Wu trusts you.

29:14.820 --> 29:15.990
How do you know that?

29:18.870 --> 29:20.300
From Liangzhou to Shuozhou,

29:20.710 --> 29:22.150
the battles were hard.

29:23.190 --> 29:24.670
But after winning these battles,

29:24.990 --> 29:26.100
Wu Shengliu trusts you.

29:26.580 --> 29:28.150
Even captains in the camp

29:28.470 --> 29:30.100
and all the soldiers in your army

29:30.470 --> 29:32.060
genuinely trust you, too.

29:33.020 --> 29:34.020
Are you saying

29:34.500 --> 29:35.430
you have

29:35.580 --> 29:36.670
full confidence in me?

29:38.260 --> 29:39.190
Now that you know

29:39.190 --> 29:40.060
I like you,

29:40.390 --> 29:41.630
I certainly have confidence...

29:43.780 --> 29:44.870
Full confidence in you.

29:47.820 --> 29:48.910
Your feelings are too strong

29:49.580 --> 29:51.100
for ordinary guys.

29:52.020 --> 29:53.020
Blowing up the river

29:53.540 --> 29:54.540
is very dangerous.

29:54.910 --> 29:56.870
One misstep will lead to the destruction

29:57.300 --> 29:58.670
and everyone will die like a dog.

29:59.340 --> 30:00.950
You're really merciless to the man

30:01.300 --> 30:02.230
you have feelings for.

30:03.060 --> 30:04.780
But you accepted that with pleasure.

30:05.870 --> 30:06.710
Are you really sure

30:06.710 --> 30:07.780
you can win this battle?

30:09.190 --> 30:10.500
If I were 100% sure,

30:11.100 --> 30:12.470
I wouldn't be a good gambler.

30:13.390 --> 30:15.020
You're a mad gambler, indeed.

30:25.120 --> 30:28.610
♪Wander to the other shore
with the lantern♪

30:28.780 --> 30:31.230
♪Accompanied by eternity♪

30:31.230 --> 30:32.340
(Well, he's also a gambler,)

30:32.340 --> 30:33.580
(cheerful and kind-hearted.)

30:35.740 --> 30:39.260
♪Love and hate will fade away♪

30:39.260 --> 30:44.500
(Liang)

30:44.540 --> 30:45.380
General.

30:47.540 --> 30:48.380
What's up?

30:49.470 --> 30:50.820
Have you met me before?

30:51.300 --> 30:53.390
About five or six years ago.

30:55.500 --> 30:56.340
Why do you ask?

30:57.230 --> 30:58.500
If we have met before,

30:58.780 --> 30:59.990
why can't you remember?

31:00.470 --> 31:01.990
At that time, I was badly injured.

31:02.950 --> 31:04.430
That's how I got this scar on my face.

31:04.990 --> 31:05.830
After I recovered,

31:06.080 --> 31:06.950
I forgot everything

31:06.950 --> 31:07.990
about my past.

31:08.540 --> 31:09.430
I didn't know

31:09.430 --> 31:10.270
you suffered that.

31:11.260 --> 31:12.820
But at that time, I was in Daizhou

31:14.060 --> 31:14.950
and I didn't see you.

31:28.710 --> 31:29.550
Simu.

31:30.990 --> 31:31.830
Take a seat.

31:35.640 --> 31:37.340
I brought you a human gadget.

31:37.580 --> 31:38.470
You'll love it.

31:42.100 --> 31:42.990
This is tea-whisking.

31:53.710 --> 31:54.710
I once saw some mortals

31:54.710 --> 31:55.630
make tea like this.

31:57.990 --> 31:59.020
It's nice to do it myself.

32:23.780 --> 32:24.740
The first pour

32:25.190 --> 32:26.470
shouldn't exceed 40% of the cup.

32:43.710 --> 32:44.990
Yan, you must be busy lately.

32:45.740 --> 32:47.580
Jiang Ai doesn't like to take charge.

32:48.740 --> 32:49.740
You have to handle

32:49.740 --> 32:50.820
all the affairs in the Void.

32:51.150 --> 32:51.990
You work too hard.

32:52.540 --> 32:54.020
War has raged in the Mortal World.

32:54.430 --> 32:55.580
Fusang Tree was unusual.

32:56.150 --> 32:57.300
But I've taken care of it.

32:58.100 --> 32:59.580
When I supervise in the Spirit World,

33:00.020 --> 33:01.150
you can enjoy your vacation

33:01.470 --> 33:02.340
and have fun.

33:17.260 --> 33:18.100
The tea tastes good.

33:20.230 --> 33:21.630
You always pick up quickly

33:22.020 --> 33:23.150
these human gadgets.

33:23.500 --> 33:24.540
It's a nice present.

33:25.060 --> 33:25.900
I'll take it.

33:26.300 --> 33:27.500
I knew you'd like it.

33:32.870 --> 33:34.400
A mortal easily gets tired.

33:34.580 --> 33:36.300
You need to eat and sleep regularly.

33:37.950 --> 33:38.790
Yeah.

33:40.670 --> 33:41.840
This body

33:42.100 --> 33:43.430
is especially hard to tend.

33:49.300 --> 33:50.140
I've been out too long.

33:50.390 --> 33:51.340
I still have work to do.

33:51.670 --> 33:52.510
I should go.

33:54.340 --> 33:55.390
When you're here,

33:55.900 --> 33:56.740
I can spend

33:56.740 --> 33:58.020
more days in the Mortal World.

33:59.190 --> 34:00.230
If it makes you happy.

34:31.020 --> 34:31.880
Foxy

34:31.880 --> 34:33.430
blew up the river one day earlier.

34:34.750 --> 34:36.220
Quite a lot of people died.

36:50.660 --> 36:52.320
Much more spirit aura will appear

36:52.330 --> 36:53.560
on Fusang Tree.

37:40.700 --> 37:42.350
Troops from Yuzhou would cross the river

37:42.350 --> 37:43.630
to attack Shuozhou.

37:43.750 --> 37:44.990
You set up an ambush here

37:45.430 --> 37:46.300
and completed the plan

37:46.310 --> 37:47.620
to blow up the river.

37:48.750 --> 37:49.620
Foxy,

37:50.390 --> 37:51.660
did you anticipate

37:51.660 --> 37:52.990
they would launch a sneak attack?

38:04.910 --> 38:06.950
What does death look like

38:07.910 --> 38:09.020
in mortals' eyes?

38:28.540 --> 38:29.380
He Xiaoxiao.

38:34.100 --> 38:35.350
You can see me?

38:53.470 --> 38:54.540
So, you associate me

38:54.540 --> 38:55.990
with the crows.

38:59.270 --> 39:00.110
He Xiaoxiao,

39:01.470 --> 39:02.310
are you here?

39:07.540 --> 39:08.830
Ever since then,

39:10.310 --> 39:11.660
you've noticed me.

39:16.140 --> 39:17.100
The time is right.

39:20.140 --> 39:21.950
Soldiers, follow my orders.

39:22.030 --> 39:22.870
Yes.

39:22.870 --> 39:24.220
How brave!

39:25.430 --> 39:27.180
A wise man avoids danger.

39:27.700 --> 39:29.700
But you get close to danger.

39:31.140 --> 39:33.310
You're just betting that I'll help.

39:44.930 --> 39:50.260
♪Between black and white,
ripples crossed♪

39:50.590 --> 39:54.840
♪Light encountered shadow♪

39:56.200 --> 40:01.570
♪It pierced the darkness and the time♪

40:01.870 --> 40:06.470
♪The unbreakable fate♪

40:07.560 --> 40:09.400
♪Suddenly cracked♪

40:12.070 --> 40:14.770
♪Listen, all sounds are roaring♪

40:14.790 --> 40:16.430
Kill!

40:16.750 --> 40:20.100
Kill!

40:20.990 --> 40:21.830
Simu,

40:22.990 --> 40:24.060
Aunt has got you

40:24.060 --> 40:24.900
a present.

40:25.500 --> 40:26.750
Maybe one day,

40:27.270 --> 40:28.390
you will meet a spell bearer

40:28.390 --> 40:30.350
who can connect with your five senses.

40:31.310 --> 40:33.140
When that person appears,

40:33.870 --> 40:35.470
the Pearl will let you know.

41:22.990 --> 41:24.390
(I'm alive and dead.)

41:25.500 --> 41:26.350
(For 400 years,)

41:26.350 --> 41:27.830
(I've never had five senses.)

41:29.990 --> 41:30.910
(I thought I'd never)

41:30.910 --> 41:32.950
(know how it felt to be alive.)

41:36.620 --> 41:37.540
(But surprisingly,)

41:39.580 --> 41:40.790
(the man who can)

41:40.790 --> 41:41.630
(give me five senses)

41:42.100 --> 41:42.990
(has appeared.)

41:51.361 --> 41:56.691
♪Between black and white,
ripples crossed♪

41:57.021 --> 42:01.271
♪Light encountered shadow♪

42:02.631 --> 42:08.001
♪It pierced the darkness and the time♪

42:08.301 --> 42:12.901
♪The unbreakable fate♪

42:13.991 --> 42:15.831
♪Suddenly cracked♪

42:28.041 --> 42:33.481
♪Between black and white,
ripples crossed♪

42:33.661 --> 42:37.991
♪Light encountered shadow♪

42:39.361 --> 42:44.751
♪It pierced the darkness and the time♪

42:44.981 --> 42:48.921
♪The unbreakable fate♪

42:50.691 --> 42:52.581
♪Suddenly cracked♪

42:55.241 --> 42:58.401
♪Listen, all sounds are roaring♪

42:58.401 --> 43:00.931
♪As cold ice turns into tides♪

43:00.931 --> 43:06.451
♪A century's loneliness melts dreams♪

43:06.451 --> 43:09.691
♪Following fate's guidance♪

43:09.691 --> 43:14.551
♪By fate, our moments were exchanged♪

43:14.891 --> 43:17.911
♪The heart wakes up all of a sudden♪

43:17.911 --> 43:20.731
♪Watch fireworks fall like stars♪

43:20.991 --> 43:23.521
♪This bond is tangled into a thread♪

43:23.521 --> 43:28.941
♪Worldly reflections fade into mist♪

43:29.111 --> 43:32.181
♪Borrowing one fleeting heartbeat♪

43:32.341 --> 43:37.241
♪You drew me into mortal dust,
till I'm enamored with its charms♪

43:37.451 --> 43:40.921
♪The heart wakes up all of a sudden♪
